            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "On closer look I think there's a problem - the GC is a per-interpreter bool. So if multiple threads are using this context manager they'll just end up conflicting.\n\nI don't think there's a good way around this so I may have to abandon this as a bad idea. But I may ask and see if there's anything to do.",
